item.title: CVE-2023-32983|2024-08-02T15:32:46.606Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20ansible%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Ansible Plugin 204.v8191fd551eb_f and earlier does not mask extra variables displayed on the configuration form, increasing the potential for attackers to observe and capture them.

item.title: CVE-2023-32982|2024-08-02T15:32:46.469Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20ansible%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Ansible Plugin 204.v8191fd551eb_f and earlier stores extra variables unencrypted in job config.xml files on the Jenkins controller where they can be viewed by users with Item/Extended Read permission or access to the Jenkins controller file system.
